We're All Just PUPPETS?!? - INSIDE ►► http://bit.ly/GTinside1

Frozen is back and... Weirder than ever? We're playing some of the craziest, derpiest, strangest Frozen themed games ever. Elsa is pregnant... Anna needs a pedicure... Elsa is a ROCKER?! Yeah crazy stuff. Just when I thought I've seen it all.
